text: Naumburg (Saale) Ost station is a railway station in the eastern part in the town of Naumburg, located in the Burgenlandkreis district in Saxony-Anhalt, Germany. ==References== ==External links== Category:Railway stations in Saxony-Anhalt Category:Buildings and structures in Burgenlandkreis
title: Naumburg (Saale) Ost station
